HEADWORD: Jarl
<hw>Jarl</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Icel., nobleman,
chief. See <er>Earl</er>.]</ety> <def>A chief; an earl; in English
history, one of the leaders in the Danish and Norse invasions.</def>
<rj><au>Longfellow.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
